acceptance_criteria: Test reads all packages/pm-*/extensions/*/manifest.json and asserts non-empty pm_min_version + integer manifest_version; failure names the offending file; in vitest include; runs in static gate.
value: "After declaring pm_min_version, a governance test (like coverage-allowlist/marketplace drift-lock) prevents future omission as package count grows."
